## Technology Stack Recommendations

### Core Platform Architecture

**Customer Relationship Management:**
- *Primary:* HubSpot (comprehensive features, good for scaling)
- *Alternative:* Salesforce (enterprise-grade, highly customizable)
- *Budget Option:* Pipedrive (cost-effective, solid functionality)

**Project and Resource Management:**
- *Primary:* Monday.com (excellent for service businesses)
- *Alternative:* Asana (strong collaboration features)
- *Specialized:* Harvest + Forecast (time tracking + resource planning)

**Financial Management:**
- *Primary:* Xero (excellent for Kenyan businesses, multi-currency)
- *Integration:* Receipt Bank (expense automation)
- *Analytics:* Fathom (financial analysis and reporting)

**Communication and Collaboration:**
- *Internal:* Slack or Microsoft Teams
- *Client:* Client portal within CRM or dedicated solution
- *Document Management:* Google Workspace or Microsoft 365

### Integration and Automation Tools

**Process Automation:**
- *Primary:* Zapier (connects most business applications)
- *Advanced:* Microsoft Power Automate (more sophisticated workflows)
- *Specialized:* Integromat/Make (complex automation scenarios)

**Analytics and Business Intelligence:**
- *Dashboard Creation:* Tableau or Power BI
- *Data Integration:* FiveTran or Stitch Data
- *Custom Analytics:* Google Analytics + Google Data Studio

